  Level 1 - Pulse    Level  9 - Toxin    Level 17 - Zombi
  Level 2 - Goose    Level 10 - Princ    Level 18 - Moves
  Level 3 - Sport    Level 11 - Clean    Level 19 - Blade
  Level 4 - Bimbo    Level 12 - Xenon    Level 20 - Zorro
  Level 5 - Tempo    Level 13 - Signs    Level 21 - Stone
  Level 6 - Baron    Level 14 - House    Level 22 - Mosel
  Level 7 - Bumm     Level 15 - Sigma    Level 23 - Order
  Level 8 - Level    Level 16 - Seven    Level 24 - Sodem
@endnode
@node "HOI"
HOI

On the level access screen, place the LVL mouse pointer in the far bottom
right of the green quarter screen.  The bottom L must be positioned in the
corner with pixel perfect precision (two pixels on the pointer will be
hanging over the edge to the right).  Click the left mouse button, then
shift the LVL mouse pointer to the very top left of the screen (as far as you
can physically over the mouse to the top left) and click the left mouse
button again.  You should now have access to the first four levels.
@endnode
@node "HOLLYWOOD POKER PRO"
HOLLYWOOD POKER PRO

Hold down 'H' and 'F9' at the same time and 100 credits will go from your
opponents account to your own.
@endnode
@node "HOOK"
HOOK

Go to the Bait and Tackle shop and pick up the mug next to the candle.  Then
keep doing 'pick up' in the space where the mug was and you'll get all the
items you need to complete the game.
@endnode
@node "HORROR ZOMBIES FROM CRYPT"
HORROR ZOMBIES FROM CRYPT

To help ease up on the terror, hold down the `M' and `.' keys for infinite
lives.  To skip levels type: "CHEATMODE" during play and 'F10' will then take
you to the next level.

These are the access codes for the various levels:

  Level 1 - Just hit return    Level 4 - LUGOSI
  Level 2 - WOLFMAN            Level 5 - NOSFERATU
  Level 3 - HAMMER             Level 6 - GARLIC

Type in BOGEYMAN for infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "HUDSON HAWK"
HUDSON HAWK

Type: "SCIENCEFICTION" (no spaces) on title screen for infinite everything.
Press the 'DELETE' key to skip levels.

Type: "SANITYCLAUSISCOMINGTOTOWN" (no spaces) for infinite lives.
@endnode
